01:11:19.192 --> 01:11:22.892
are observing these ongoing chromosome segregation through single cell genomics to

1241
01:11:22.952 --> 01:11:26.672
validate it by imaging. To do this, what we did is we used

1242
01:11:26.812 --> 01:11:26.952
a

1243
01:11:28.172 --> 01:11:31.192
