1271
01:13:03.332 --> 01:13:07.242
doubling. So once the cells become genome doubled, they have such high levels of

1272
01:13:07.272 --> 01:13:10.322
instability that they need to down-regulate cGAS-STING signaling as a

1273
01:13:11.032 --> 01:13:13.132
