01:13:52.372 --> 01:13:56.142
and whether there's ongoing diversification happening from additional

1285
01:13:56.172 --> 01:13:57.612
events in the metastatic,

1286
01:13:58.672 --> 01:14:02.192
in the peritoneal cavity. So in all these other sites that you can see

1287
01:14:02.232 --> 01:14:06.112
intermixed in this heat map that seem to be diversifying

1288
01:14:06.212 --> 01:14:08.012
